data.description: Beautiful recently renovated home with private pool, garage and driveway space! It offers three cozy bedrooms, two bright and functional bathrooms with two separate entertaining spaces to entertain guest and family! Beautiful view of pool from primary bedroom. New tile throughout the home, updated exterior touches and well-kept yard. The home is a short drive from the Turnpike, I95, Ft Lauderdale Airport, Broward park, Hollywood Guitar Hotel, Malls and the Sunny Beaches. Refrigerator, and outdoor camera's are excluded from sale. Currently owner occupied. Please feel free to reach out to discuss offers!!!! No Cash offers less than $10,000 of asking!! Submit offers with POF, and approval letter.
